<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <main class="main-container">

    <section class="hero-section">
      <h1 class="hero-title"><%= __('hero_title') %></h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        <%- __('hero_subtitle') %>
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="grid-container">

      <div>
        <h2 class="section-title-blue"><%= __('about_page.journey_title') %></h2>
        <p class="content-text"><%- __('about_page.journey_p1') %></p>
        <p class="content-text"><%- __('about_page.journey_p2') %></p>
        <p class="content-text"><%- __('about_page.journey_p3') %></p>
        <p class="content-text"><%- __('about_page.journey_p4') %></p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="section-title-green"><%= __('about_page.beyond_title') %></h2>

        <div class="image-wrapper">
          <img src="/img/sait-mentor.jpg" alt="Sait Elmas" class="profile-image">
        </div>

        <p class="content-text"><%- __('about_page.beyond_p1') %></p>
        <p class="content-text"><%- __('about_page.beyond_p2') %></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="testimonials-section">
      <h2 class="testimonials-title"><%= __('about_page.testimonials_title') %></h2>

      <div class="testimonial-container">
        <div class="testimonial-track">

          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
            <p class="student-text">Sait teacher's engineering perspective made AP Calculus incredibly easy to understand. He doesn't just teach formulas; he teaches how to think. Thanks to him, I got a 5 on my exam.</p>
            <div class="student-name">Deniz K.</div>
            <div class="student-school">Admitted to Technical University of Munich</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
            <p class="student-text">The transition from high school math to university Linear Algebra was tough, but his clear, logical explanations saved my GPA. Highly recommended for any engineering student.</p>
            <div class="student-name">Can B.</div>
            <div class="student-school">Computer Engineering Student</div>
          </div>

          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
            <p class="student-text">I was struggling with IB Physics HL. His method of breaking down complex physical phenomena into simple mathematical models is truly unique.</p>
            <div class="student-name">Ayşe Y.</div>
            <div class="student-school">IB Diploma Graduate</div>
          </div>

          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
            <p class="student-text">He helped me structure my entire approach to Java and OOP. Beyond just passing my CS classes, he gave me the vision to actually enjoy coding and software design.</p>
            <div class="student-name">Emre T.</div>
            <div class="student-school">University CS Student</div>
          </div>

          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
            <p class="student-text">I am taking AP Calculus lessons, and he is a truly great teacher. The methods he teaches are memorable, and because he introduces new approaches, my perspective on solving questions has genuinely changed.</p>
            <div class="student-name">Elif V.</div>
            <div class="student-school">AP Calculus Student</div>
          </div>

          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
            <p class="student-text">I have been taking AP and IB lessons from Sait teacher for 2 years. He explains topics simply and clearly, patiently repeating parts I don't understand. His communication with students is excellent.</p>
            <div class="student-name">Kaan B.</div>
            <div class="student-school">AP & IB Computer Science Student</div>
          </div>

          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
            <p class="student-text">He is a very attentive and highly equipped instructor. He explains topics through logic rather than memorization. His simple explanations make even the hardest topics easily understandable.</p>
            <div class="student-name">Edibe Ö.</div>
            <div class="student-school">IB Mathematics Student</div>
          </div>

          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
            <p class="student-text">I requested support for my son studying Computer Engineering in the Netherlands. My son was incredibly satisfied, noting Sait teacher's excellent communication and profound expertise in computer science.</p>
            <div class="student-name">Halil K.</div>
            <div class="student-school">Parent of a University CS Student</div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>